Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, March 28 (KCNA) -- The March 21 statement 
of a spokesman for the Foreign Ministry of the Democratic 
People's Republic of Korea denouncing the United States for its 
perfidious act in totally reversing the February 25 agreed 
conclusions reached at the DPRK-U.S. contact in New York was 
distributed on March 22 as an official document S/1994/327 of 
the United Nations Security Council. 

